title: Correction to: Relative role of community transmission and campus contagion in driving the spread of SARS-CoV-2: Lessons from Princeton University
content: This is a correction to: Sang Woo Park, Irini Daskalaki, Robin M Izzo, Irina Aranovich, Aartjan J W te Velthuis, Daniel A Notterman, C Jessica E Metcalf, Bryan T Grenfell, Relative role of community transmission and campus contagion in driving the spread of SARS-CoV-2: Lessons from Princeton University, PNAS Nexus, Volume 2, Issue 7, July 2023, pgad201, https://doi.org/10.1093/pnasnexus/pgad201
